      "instruction": "<p>Once the potatoes are tender, drain and return to the pot with 2<span class=\"text-purple\"> [3]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[4]</span> knobs of <strong>butter</strong>, a splash of <strong>milk</strong>,<strong> </strong>a very generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper </strong>and<strong> </strong>mash until smooth</p><p>Separate the <strong>egg yolk[s]</strong> from the <strong>white[s]</strong> by cracking your <strong>egg[s]</strong> over a small bowl and catching the yolk in the shell</p><p>Add the<strong> egg yolk[s]</strong> (save the whites for another recipe!) and <strong>chopped garlic</strong> to the mashed potatoes and give everything a good mix up until well combined – this is your <strong>potato mix</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
