    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Transfer the <strong>potato mix</strong> to a small<strong> oven-proof dish</strong> (reserve the pot!) and discard the <strong>bay leaf[ves]</strong></p><p>Press the back of a spoon into the mix to make rows of ridges</p><p>Put the dish in oven and cook for 15-20 min or until slightly crispy and golden – these are your <strong>duchess potatoes</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
