    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the green beans have had 10 min, remove the tray[s] from the oven and add your <strong>walnuts</strong></p><p>Return the tray[s] to the oven and cook for a final 3-4 min or until the walnuts are toasted – this is your <strong>roast duck, confit shallots, roast veg & toasted walnuts</strong></p><p>Tip: Watch the walnuts like a hawk to make sure they don’t burn!</p>",
