    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>roast duck legs </strong>with<strong> </strong>the <strong>confit shallots</strong>,<strong> </strong>and the<strong> roast veg </strong>topped with the<strong> toasted walnuts</strong></p><p>Serve the <strong>duchess potatoes</strong> and <strong>red wine & duck jus </strong>all in the centre of the table</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
